    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing exactly as it did the day it was delivered from the factory. The paint is flawless with no chips or scratches, and the interior retains its original showroom scent with no signs of wear on the upholstery. Every mechanical component functions perfectly, and the engine bay is spotlessly clean. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment.",
